        "subheading": "<p><strong>Celebrating Creativity</strong></p>",
        "title": "<p>Artist In Residency </p>",
        "description": "<p>At Natalie Marie Jewellery, we celebrate creativity in all its forms. Our <em>Artist in Residency</em> program offers a platform for local Australian artists to showcase their work within our showrooms — transforming our spaces into evolving galleries of art and craftsmanship.</p><p>Each season, we feature a new artist whose work aligns with our values of intentional creation and thoughtful design. Their pieces are available to view and purchase in-store and online, offering our community the opportunity to connect with art that inspires and uplifts.</p><p>We invite you to experience the beauty of local artistry on your next visit.</p>",
        "feature_text": "<p>Where jewellery meets art — featuring  artists in residence, exclusively in our showrooms.</p>",
